article.description: — Travis Evee had 24 points, eight rebounds and eight assists as Rice rolled past Incarnate Word 85-55 on Thursday.
article.headline: Evee scores 24 to lead Rice over Incarnate Word 85-55
article.linkText: Evee scores 24 to lead Rice over Incarnate Word 85-55
article.story: HOUSTON -- — Travis Evee had 24 points, eight rebounds and eight assists as Rice rolled past Incarnate Word 85-55 on Thursday. Evee hit 6 of 8 3-pointers. Carl Pierre added 14 points and Mylyjael Poteat had 13 for Rice (7-4). Drew Lutz scored a season-high 21 points for the Cardinals (2-9). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
